#!/usr/bin/env libui
#####
#
#	Create Package
#
#	F Harvell - Wed Feb 16 19:59:57 EST 2022
#
#####
#
# Used to create a self-extracting package from a file list.
#
# Man page available for this script: man 1 createpackage
#
#####
#
